          "slidetitle": "Red Flags to Watch For",
          "subtitle": "Warning signs clinicians must recognise now",
          "slidecontent": "• AI sounds overly confident\n• No source cited\n• Rare conditions missed\n• Contradicts your training\n• Output never questioned"
