          "subtitle": "Core principles for safer AI use",
          "slidecontent": "• AI assists, never decides\n• Always verify AI output\n• Patient safety comes first\n• Escalate when uncertain\n• You hold clinical responsibility\n• Speak up, stay vigilant"
